#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/open_solder.rst:2
msgid "开焊检测（Open Solder）"
msgstr "Open Solder Inspection"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/open_solder.rst:4
msgid "**此页面的用途**"
msgstr "**What this page covers**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/open_solder.rst:6
msgid "检测焊点开路 / 未连接（虚焊、空焊）等缺陷。"
msgstr ""
"Detects open-circuit solder joints — unsoldered, insufficiently-soldered, or "
"cold-solder defects."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/open_solder.rst:8
msgid "**如何进入**"
msgstr "**How to open it**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/open_solder.rst:10
msgid "模板编辑器中绘制对应 ROI 后，在参数面板中配置该工具的参数。"
msgstr ""
"Draw the corresponding ROI in the Template Editor, then configure the tool's "
"parameters in the parameter panel."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/open_solder.rst:12
msgid "**操作流程**"
msgstr "**Workflow**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/open_solder.rst:-1
msgid "模板编辑器中的开焊检测元件示例"
msgstr "Example of an Open Solder inspection component in the Template Editor"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/open_solder.rst:18
msgid "**启用开焊检测（Enable Open Solder Inspection）**：开关该检测项。"
msgstr "**Enable Open Solder Inspection**: toggle this inspection on or off."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/open_solder.rst:19
msgid "**置信度阈值（Confidence Threshold）**：模型判定门限。"
msgstr "**Confidence Threshold**: decision threshold for the model."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/open_solder.rst:20
msgid "**自定义模型（Custom Model）/ 自定义模型路径（Custom Model Path）**：选用自定义训练模型。"
msgstr ""
"**Custom Model / Custom Model Path**: select a custom-trained model to use "
"instead of the default."
